      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A Dependable Daily Driver \u2014 Honestly Priced for Real Value!\n\nThis vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably, drives as expected, and will handle your everyday commute without complaint. We believe in full transparency: the exterior shows visible wear and there are some cosmetic imperfections inside and out, as you'd expect from a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, it does what it needs to do, making it a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer who needs dependable transportation without paying for perfection. No surprises here \u2014 just a straightforward, honest car at a fair price!",
